## Web routes

- Community hub link + **`/meriter/communities/[id]/documents`** (list), **`/meriter/communities/[id]/documents/[documentId]`** (detail).
- Proposal/editor: TipTap **`RichTextEditor`**; display: **`DocumentRichContent`** (sanitize); legacy plain variants still render safely.

